snippet.title: SimplePlanes VR is now available on Steam and Oculus Quest 1 & 2
snippet.description:
We hope you enjoy your flight! Get SimplePlanes VR today on Steam and Oculus Quest 1 & 2. 
Oculus Quest: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5939612999412499/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1692700/SimplePlanes_VR/

This video was created by @Vincent. You can check out his YouTube channel here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCun38IipApBUzgKWZBgiWmA
